  <bioghist id="aspace_22479d98b7b39863d51d15d664c15a74">
    <head>Historical/Biographical Note</head>
<p>Seymour and Vera Steinsapir were Young People's Socialist League and Socialist Party members beginning in the 1930s. Seymour was frequently a member of the National Action Committee in the 1950s and 1960s and was later a leader of the Debs Caucus.</p>  </bioghist>
